cypher_translation: MATCH (p1:Protein)-[:ProteinInteractsWithProtein]->(p2:Protein {displayName: 'P53_HUMAN'}) RETURN DISTINCT p1.displayName AS InteractingProtein

nl_question: Which gene encodes the protein 'EGFR', and what is its approved symbol and chromosome?
cypher_translation: MATCH (p:Protein {displayName: 'EGFR_HUMAN'})-[:ProteinEncodedByGene]->(g:Gene ) RETURN g.approvedSymbol AS ApprovedSymbol, g.chromosome AS Chromosome

nl_question: In which biological pathways is the protein 'MYC_HUMAN' involved, and for what species are these pathways listed?
cypher_translation: MATCH (p:Protein)-[:ProteinInPathway]->(pw:Pathway) WHERE p.displayName = 'MYC_HUMAN' RETURN pw.displayName AS PathwayName, pw.species AS Species

nl_question: In which tissues is the protein 'CFTR_HUMAN' expressed?
cypher_translation: MATCH (p:Protein)-[:ProteinExpressedInTissue]->(t:Tissue) WHERE p.displayName = 'CFTR_HUMAN' RETURN t.displayName AS TissueName
